                        <div class="fbcms_content fbcms_richtext home_right" id="content_40082">
    <div class="fbcms_richtext_content">
        <h2>Schools of Choice and New Student Registration 2020-2021</h2>

<p><span>School of Choice applications may be submitted beginning April 13 - June 1, 2020.  Applications can be filled out, signed electronically and emailed to lnava@cppschools.com or mailed to 101 School St NE, Comstock Park 49321</span><span>.  For more details and numbers of openings available <a href="/parents/schools-of-choice/">click here</a>.</span></p>

<p><a href="/downloads/district/soc_brochure_20-21_-_revised.pdf" target="_blank">Kent County Schools of Choice Brochure</a></p>

<p><a href="/downloads/district/soc_application_electronic_2020-2021.docx" target="_blank">School of Choice application - English</a></p>

<p><a href="/downloads/district/soc_application_hard_copy_spanish_2020-2021.docx" target="_blank">School of Choice application - Spanish</a></p>

<p><a href="/downloads/district/20-21_105c_application_english.docx" target="_blank">105C out of county school of choice application - English</a></p>

<p><a href="/downloads/district/20-21_105c_application_spanish.docx" target="_blank">105C out of county school of choice application - Spanish</a></p>

<p>Questions or assistance with the application process can be directed to Lisa Nava. Phone - (616)254-5018 or Email - lnava@cppschools.com</p>

<h3> </h3>

<h3>New Student Enrollment for  2020-2021</h3>

<p>Enrollment for the 2020-2021 School Year is now open and requires two easy steps:</p>

<p>  1.  Fill out the School Enrollment form by clicking on one of the following links:</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="https://secure.infosnap.com/family/gosnap.aspx?action=22714&amp;culture=en" target="_blank">Comstock Park Registration Form - English</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://secure.infosnap.com/family/gosnap.aspx?action=22714&amp;culture=es" target="_blank">Comstock Park Registration Form - Spanish</a></li>
</ul>
<p>  2.  Make an appointment to complete enrollment.</p>

<p>* Due to mandatory school closures there will  be no appointments at this time.  You will be contacted with next steps once we receive your application.  </p>

<p>* If your student is currently in the Little Panthers Preschool or Early Childhood Special Education Program you do not need to do a new student registration but will need to do a returning student registration when it opens in May.</p>

<h3>Returning Student Enrollment for 2020-2021 will be open mid May.  You will receive an email when it is ready.</h3>

<p>Please log in to your <a href="https://powerschool.cppschools.com/public/" target="_blank">Powerschool parent account</a> to complete the returning registration for each of your children.  Once you are logged in to the portal, click on the "Returning Student Registration" link from the menu on the left and follow the prompts. </p>
